---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Autism Signals | Visual Mockups"
  description="Three visual directions for the What this covers panel."
>
  <main class="page-shell mockup-shell">
    <section class="mockup-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Visual Directions</p>
      <h1>Three mockups for the “What this covers” panel.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        These are side-by-side directions for the top-right card: one brand-led pattern,
        one ultra-clean texture treatment, and one more editorial composition.
      </p>
      <p class="body-copy">
        My recommendation is the <strong>Signal Wave</strong> direction because it feels
        distinctive, on-brand with “Autism Signals,” and premium without drifting into
        stock-photo territory.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mockup-grid">
      <article class="mock-card">
        <div class="mock-card__head">
          <span class="mock-badge mock-badge--recommended">Recommended</span>
          <strong>Signal Wave</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="mock-cover mock-cover--signal">
          <div class="mock-cover__content">
            <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--soft">What this covers</p>
            <h2>Professional tone, clear boundaries, and useful reflection.</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Clear prompts about social interpretation, masking, routines, sensory profile, and focus.</li>
              <li>Results that stay careful about uncertainty and never claim to diagnose, validate, or officially screen for autism.</li>
              <li>Optional note-taking so someone can keep track of patterns, questions, and support needs.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mock-note">
          Best balance of brand identity, calmness, and polish. Feels custom to the
          product without overwhelming the content.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mock-card">
        <div class="mock-card__head">
          <span class="mock-badge">Minimal</span>
          <strong>Paper Texture</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="mock-cover mock-cover--paper">
          <div class="mock-cover__content">
            <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--soft">What this covers</p>
            <h2>Professional tone, clear boundaries, and useful reflection.</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Clear prompts about social interpretation, masking, routines, sensory profile, and focus.</li>
              <li>Results that stay careful about uncertainty and never claim to diagnose, validate, or officially screen for autism.</li>
              <li>Optional note-taking so someone can keep track of patterns, questions, and support needs.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mock-note">
          The safest and most understated option. It keeps the UI very premium while
          adding only a whisper of pattern and warmth.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mock-card">
        <div class="mock-card__head">
          <span class="mock-badge">Editorial</span>
          <strong>Light Panel</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="mock-cover mock-cover--editorial">
          <div class="mock-cover__content">
            <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--soft">What this covers</p>
            <h2>Professional tone, clear boundaries, and useful reflection.</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Clear prompts about social interpretation, masking, routines, sensory profile, and focus.</li>
              <li>Results that stay careful about uncertainty and never claim to diagnose, validate, or officially screen for autism.</li>
              <li>Optional note-taking so someone can keep track of patterns, questions, and support needs.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mock-note">
          More art-directed and magazine-like. This gives the section a stronger visual
          identity while still avoiding generic people photography.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .mockup-shell {
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .mockup-intro {
    max-width: 78ch;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mockup-intro h1 {
    margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
    font-family: 'Iowan Old Style', 'Palatino Linotype', 'Book Antiqua', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .mockup-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .mock-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .mock-card__head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .mock-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 2rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted-strong);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mock-badge--recommended {
    background: rgba(14, 78, 77, 0.12);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .mock-cover {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 38rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82), rgba(236, 246, 245, 0.88));
  }

  .mock-cover__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 1.8rem;
  }

  .mock-cover h2 {
    margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
    font-family: 'Iowan Old Style', 'Palatino Linotype', 'Book Antiqua', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    max-width: 10ch;
  }

  .mock-cover ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 28ch;
  }

  .mock-cover li + li {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
  }

  .mock-note {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .mock-cover--signal {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 16% 18%, rgba(197, 127, 68, 0.16), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(155deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82), rgba(236, 246, 245, 0.88));
  }

  .mock-cover--signal::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -10% -14% auto auto;
    width: 78%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background:
      repeating-radial-gradient(
        circle at center,
        rgba(14, 78, 77, 0.08) 0 2px,
        transparent 2px 26px
      );
    opacity: 0.7;
    transform: translate(6%, -2%);
  }

  .mock-cover--signal::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: auto auto 6% -6%;
    width: 42%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 78, 77, 0.12), transparent 72%);
    filter: blur(2px);
  }

  .mock-cover--paper {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 78% 84%, rgba(14, 78, 77, 0.08), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(244, 239, 231, 0.92));
  }

  .mock-cover--paper::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(rgba(18, 42, 56, 0.05) 0.8px, transparent 0.8px),
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18));
    background-size: 18px 18px, auto;
    opacity: 0.5;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .mock-cover--paper::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10% 8% auto auto;
    width: 54%;
    height: 42%;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35), rgba(197, 127, 68, 0.08));
    filter: blur(28px);
  }

  .mock-cover--editorial {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(240, 248, 247, 0.9));
  }

  .mock-cover--editorial::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0 0 0 56%;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), rgba(14, 78, 77, 0.04)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 28% 24%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95), transparent 22%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 64% 62%, rgba(197, 127, 68, 0.18), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(220, 234, 232, 0.9), rgba(241, 233, 222, 0.92));
  }

  .mock-cover--editorial::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 12% 7% 12% 58%;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background:
      linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35), transparent 52%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 42, 56, 0.06), rgba(18, 42, 56, 0));
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45),
      0 20px 36px rgba(16, 31, 43, 0.08);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .mockup-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mock-cover {
      min-height: 28rem;
    }

    .mock-cover h2,
    .mock-cover ul {
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
</style>
